ANC has bashed Jubilee for planning to allow the IEBC to conduct its primaries.Coast secretary general Jimmy Azangu said the electoral agency has &ldquo;a bad reputation and engaging it in primaries might dent its image more&rdquo;.He said the IEBC&rsquo;s credibility failed after it conducted the &ldquo;shambolic&rdquo; 2013 general election.